ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Acknowledging Receipt of the Assessments Done Pursuant to Subsection 23(1) of the Act
PrecisORDER ACKNOWLEDGING RECEIPT OF THE ASSESSMENTS DONE PURSUANT TO SUBSECTION 23(1) OF THE ACT, for which, (1) eight species were assessed and classified as being endangered, threatened or of special concern; (2) two are reclassifications of a species already on the List; and (3) one is a listed wildlife species currently assessed as not at risk.
